    "title": "京东开放平台医药类目资质标准",
    "followRuleId": "3709",
    "content": "<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 100%; background: white; border-collapse: collapse; border: none; line-height: 2;\" border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 100.0%; border: inset black 1.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" colspan=\"4\" width=\"100%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">招商说明：<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">非处方药、处方药实物类目仅开放旗舰店入驻开店，接受连锁总部、连锁分店、单体药房入驻开店。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">品牌旗舰店（只对药企开放，只允许经营授权的药品品牌，需提供对应的产品明细）：授权药房不受年限限制，需提供药品5类商标/5类商标+独占授权书。<br />2. 大药房旗舰店（可经营多品牌产品）：同一入驻开店公司只允许开设3家大药房旗舰店，需提供35类服务类商标注册证或商标注册申请受理通知书（连锁药房可用药品经营许可证+门头照片代替）。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3. TM</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">标入驻开店要求注册申请时间至开店审核时间必须大于3个月，TM标有效期请填写申请日期加2年后的日期，R标有效期按商标注册证有效日期填写。专卖店、专营店接受3级以内授权（含3级）。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 10.14%; border: inset black 1.0pt; border-top: none; background: #BA372A; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"10%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">一级类目</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.1%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: inset black 1.0pt; border-right: inset black 1.0pt; background: #BA372A; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">二级类目</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.06%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: inset black 1.0pt; border-right: inset black 1.0pt; background: #BA372A; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">行业资质</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 31.7%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: inset black 1.0pt; background: #BA372A; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"31%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">特殊资质及要求</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 10.14%; border: inset black 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"3\" width=\"10%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">医药</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.1%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: inset black 1.0pt; border-right: inset black 1.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">在线问诊-互联网宠物医院（三级类目）</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.06%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: inset black 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、需</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">提供开店公司《</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">动物诊疗许可证》</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《执业兽医备案表</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">》：</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">执业兽医需备案在开店公司</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 31.7%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"31%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 29.1%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: inset black 1.0pt; border-right: inset black 1.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">非处方药</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.06%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: inset black 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《药品经营许可证》，经营范围要严格包含经营品类，经营方式需包含零售。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、提供开店公司药品质量管理体系文件（①质量保证体系调查表；②质量体系文件目录）</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 31.7%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"31%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、药师或者其他药学技术人员的资格认定证书。 </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、以连锁总部或批零兼营入驻的商家，需提供履约配送连锁门店的营业执照、药品经营许可证、药师或者其他药学技术人员的资格认定证书、药品质量管理体系文件（①质量保证体系调查表；②质量体系文件目录）。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">备注：1. 依法配备的药师是指执业药师，其证书是指执业药师注册证；2. 依法配备的其他药学技术人员包括卫生（药）系列职称（含药师、主管药师、副主任药师、主任药师）、从业药师等；其证书是指其对应的药师资格证。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 29.1%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: inset black 1.0pt; border-right: inset black 1.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">处方药（妇科专科用药、男科专科用药、风湿骨外专科用药、五官用药、泌尿系统用药、皮肤及性病用药、呼吸系统用药、肿瘤用药、内分泌用药、心脑血管用药、消化系统用药、肝胆用药、神经系统用药、抗感染用药、儿科专科用药、补益安神、解热镇痛、血液系统用药、移植用药、中药饮片、维生素/矿物质用药等）</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 100.0%; border: inset black 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" colspan=\"4\" width=\"100%\">\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">旗舰店授权书模板：</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://helpcenter.jd.com/vender/issue/926-4279.html\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; color: blue;\">旗舰店授权书模板</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东开放平台各类目资费一览表：</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=638209647311982592&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; color: blue;\">京东开放平台类目资费规则</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">店铺命名规则：</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2598\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; color: blue;\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2598</span></a></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">附则</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东商家的行为，发生在本管理规则生效之日以前的，适用当时的规则。发生在本管理规则生效之日以后的，适用本规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东可根据平台运营情况随时调整本管理规则并向商家公示。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家应遵守国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件。对任何涉嫌违反国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件的行为，本规则已有规定的，适用于本规则。本规则尚无规定的，京东有权酌情处理。但京东对商家的处理不免除其应承担的法律责任。商家在京东的任何行为，应同时遵守与京东及其关联公司签订的各项协议。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">本规则标准于2025年3月20日修订，于2025年3月27日生效。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>",
